If the client is not encoding, persisting and decoding @B_com#google#android#gms#drive#DriveId_E@s, this method will always return either @B_com#google#android#gms#drive#DriveId#RESOURCE_TYPE_FILE_E@ or @B_com#google#android#gms#drive#DriveId#RESOURCE_TYPE_FOLDER_E@.
